Package: viralORF
Type: Package
Title: Finds Viral Open Reading Frames
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hou Wei Chook
Maintainer: Hou Wei Chook <HouWei.Chook@ed.ac.uk>
Description: A streamlined toolkit developed for viral genome analysis.
    Contains custom pipelines to identify, translate, and map two 
    different definitions of an open reading frame.
